n = 4000

function newton(f,  Df, z)
    for i in 1:1000
        dz = f(z)/Df(z)
        z = z - dz
        if (abs(f(z).re) < 1.e-8 && abs(f(z).im) < 1.e-8)
            return z
        end
    end
    return false
end

function get_root_index(roots, r)
    for i in 1:length(roots)
        if(isapprox(roots[i], r))
            return i
        end
    end
    append!(roots, r)
    return length(roots)
end

domain = [-1,-1,1,1]

m = zeros(Int8, n, n)

function tmp(x,y)
    m[x,y]
end

function newton_fractal(f, df)
    roots = zeros(Complex, 0)
    for i in 1:n
        for j in 1:n
            z = domain[1]+abs(domain[1]-domain[3])/n*i + (domain[2]+abs(domain[2]-domain[4])/n*j)*im
            #print(z,"\n")
            r = newton(f, df, z)
            ri = get_root_index(roots, r)
            m[i,j] = ri
        end
    end
    heatmap([x for x in 1:n], [y for y in 1:n],tmp,c = :rainbow, size=[1000, 700])
end


f(x) = x^4-1
D(x) = 4*x^3

newton_fractal(f, D)
